source: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>Inscribed upon a metal plate are the words “Mark II crystal forge.” While the apparatus does not appear to be damaged, and it is clearly patterned after the forge in Pagos, its purpose and usage are not entirely clear...
target: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_000<tab>Vous pouvez lire l'inscription “<var 2B ((<var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61EAA2E0202 /var>)) /var>”. Probablement un dispositif en rapport avec la machine au nom similaire à Pagos. Revenez lorsque vous en aurez l'utilité.

source: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>Inscribed upon a metal plate are the words “Mark II crystal forge.” The apparatus does not appear to be damaged, and it seems simple enough to use─presuming you have sufficient vitiated aether with which to fuel its operation...
target: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>Vous pouvez lire l'inscription “<var 2B ((<var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61EAA2E0202 /var>)) /var>”. Vous devriez pouvoir l'utiliser pour transformer l'éther composite en cristaux.

source: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>It seems your Eurekan kettle lacks sufficient vitiated aether to produce even a single crystal...
target: TEXT_CTSERKEUREKA3AETHERPOT_00538_SYSTEM_000_020<tab>Vous n'avez pas accumulé assez d'éther composite pour former un cristal.
